  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="set_visibility" data-step-uuid="d4fe9224-e3cd-4208-ba1b-281fc9851c71">
    <h2 id="set_visibility" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Set Visibility</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/002/982/690/original/565a881d-8407-4052-85f3-d9e911044b75.png" srcset="" alt="Set Visibility" height="152" width="691">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_F663F0D0-22CF-0135-BC54-22000AB760A3" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In the Visibility options, the default is set to Course. </p>
<p>To change the visibility, click the <strong>Visibility </strong>menu and select the visibility option you prefer [1].</p>
<p>If the Visibility option cannot be changed, you do not have permission to manage visibility settings [2]. Please contact your Canvas administrator or Canvas Support for assistance.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
        <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-2" id="customize_content_visibility" data-step-uuid="95df41d6-e44e-4954-aa0b-e2e04a5fd1bf">
